{"tid":1633190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［後排 和理入］企疏啲之餘仲要做多樣嘢","createTime":"2019-10-07T02:53:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T04:05:51.000Z","uid":150267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dc62aa5c37d6b321c0c92e03c846a889cdd76e51","tid":1633190,"uid":150267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:53:19.000Z","msg":"唔知今日會發生咩事 <br />\n<br />\n但如果今日要落場嘅<br />\n<br />\n後排同我<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">企疏啲 </span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">兩個三個一小隊</span></span>  <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">多過三個就分兩隊</span></strong></span><br />\n一堆人企堆一齊 散既時候真係好阻到人<br />\n<br />\n落場唔係玩 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>你地既每一步都影響緊前線</strong></span></span> <br />\n前線幫你地擋曬啲彈  會俾狗咬<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人命黎</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n每個人落場既同我專心啲 係打緊杖<br />\n<br />\n無野做就睇下哨兵group 俾多啲資訊前線<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔好再亂甘叫口號</span> 前面會聽唔到哨講咩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"883e430a4c801be699d3deabd2bf0f6351284600","tid":1633190,"uid":150267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:57:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GhgTvOR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGhgTvOR.jpg&h=5ce80649&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d16827d62554eefd3a49087a012cb28a7e2abcb3","tid":1633190,"uid":150267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:58:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c4d52df7047d42a4852b9c99323249848acfd2c","tid":1633190,"uid":150267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:58:55.000Z","msg":"<img 